Analysis:
* Start-Sleep: Delay execution (evasion tactic)
* INVOKE-MossCript: Likely "Invoke-Mimikatz" or similar, obfuscated
Verdict: HIGHLY SUSPICIOUS - encoded PowerShell with delay and obfuscated command
